    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-11-25T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-11-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="1745"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1745">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 718.1915/226.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Minister of Costa Rica</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Costa Rica</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-11-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 25, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Mr. Secretary of State</hi>: I have the honor to transmit
                    to your excellency a translation of the reply which the Government of Costa Rica
                    made to the note<note n="8" xml:id="d1745fn8">The same as Inclosure 2 with Mr.
                        Cresson’s despatch No. 331 of November 18.</note> of the Government of
                    Panama, in which the <pb facs="1138" n="1022" xml:id="pg_1022"/> Minister for
                    Foreign Affairs of this country sets forth the reasons that move it to reject
                    the Award of the Chief Justice of the United States.</p>
                <p>While taking the liberty of calling your excellency’s attention to the arguments
                    made by my Government, I avail [etc.]</p>
                <closer>[Unsigned] [<signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">R. Brenes Mesén</hi>
                    </signed>.]</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
